Detailed Description

Class KeyToneAudioDevice
Class to play a key tone.
Note: Key tones can always be played.

Note: Do not use audio interface given by the *AudioDevices* header files as they are outdated and will be removed.

KeyToneAudioDevice::AudioReturnCode KeyToneAudioDevice::Start (  BOOLEAN  auto_release = TRUE  )  [virtual]
 

Plays the requested key tone using the DSP tone generator.
Key tones have the highest priority and will be played instantly.
If DSP is occupied with an other tone, the tone will be paused and resumed for the key tone.
